document.full_text: near the grave of libyan resistance hero omar al-mukhtar, insurgents have painted a wall the rebel tricolor, ripped muammar's gaddafi's name from a stone plaque and scrawled anti-government graffiti everywhere.
document.title: libyan rebels reclaim legacy of italian-era warrior
